<%= content_for :tail do %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "owners_channel","master_interviews" %>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function() {
         <%- if flash[:mix_color] %>
            $(".popupA").show();
         <%- end %>
        })
        $(".submit_xxlarge").click(function(){
           if ($('.input-xxlarge').val() == ''){
            alert('请输入具体内容!');
            return false;
          }
        })
    </script>
<%- end -%>
<div class="main" style="width:auto">
  <div class="sub_title text-right">
    <img src="<%= asset_path "design/title_owner.png" %>">
  </div>
  <div class="sub_nav ft12 pr tr">
    <em><%= link_to "配色咨询", "/mix_colors/new", :class => 'fb' %></em>
    <em><%= link_to "业主通道", "/channel/access" %><span></span></em>
    <em><%= link_to "首页", "/" %><span></span></em>
    <style type="text/css">
        span.arrow_1 {
            right: 178px;
        }

        span.arrow_2 {
            right: 110px;
        }
    </style>
  </div>
  <!--sub_nav ends-->
  <div class="wrapper group owners_channel">
    <div class="banner"><img src="<%= asset_path "news/service1.jpg" %>"></div>
    <div class="intro">
      <p>您是不是厌倦了现在的家居搭配呢？对家居的色彩搭配感到烦恼，不知该如何选择了呢？如今您大可不用担心啦！</p>

      <p>立邦挺您专业的色彩搭配资讯，根据您的家居与软装设计给出最合理，并且最适合您的色彩搭配风格。为您提供量身定制的个性化家居色彩体验，好心情让我们从家居环境开始。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="banner"><img src="<%= asset_path "news/service2.jpg" %>"></div>
    <div class="owners_form">
      <div class="title">
        <h5>我们的需求：</h5>

        <p>上传你的图片或设计稿并提出您的要求，我们会在7个工作日内为您提供个性化配色建议<b>(已有<%= @mix_size %>人咨询)</b></p>
      </div>
      <div class="form_target">
        <iframe id="upload_target" name="upload_target"></iframe>
      </div>
      <%= form_for(@mix_color, :url => pre_mix_colors_path, :html => { :id => "upload_form", :multipart => true }) do |f| %>
          <table>
            <tbody>
            <tr class="f_content">
              <th>内　　容：</th>
              <td>
                <%= f.text_area :description, :class => 'input-xxlarge'%>
                您还可以输入<span id="characters">500</span>字
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="f_image">
              <th>图片上传：</th>
              <td>
                <%= file_field(:mix_color, :mix_color_img) %>
              </td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="f_submit">
              <th>&nbsp;</th>
              <td><input type="image" src="<%= asset_path "design/submitB.gif" %>" class="submit_xxlarge" alt="提交" value="提交">
                <input type="reset" class="reset" value="重置">
              </td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
      <%- end -%>
      <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= asset_path "owners_channel_upload_form.js" %>"></script>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="popupA">
    <div class="popupA_content popupA_middle">
      <div class="popupA_title"><h4>提示</h4><span class="close"></span></div>
      <div class="popupA_body">
        <div class="success">提交成功！</div>
        <div class="desc">我们将在3个工作日内对您的色彩需求给予答复，请留意系统消息。<br>具体规则流程请查看 <a href="#">服务与介绍流程</a></div>
        <div class="button"><input type="button" class="ok okA" value="确定"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="popupA_mask"></div>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="<%= asset_path "popupA.js" %>"></script>
  <div class="sub_bot pr">
    <div class="pager ft12">
    </div>
    <!--pager ends-->
  </div>
  <!--sub_bot ends-->
</div>